        "created_at": "2006-10-20T22:38:28.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>These are the things we need to do in this project.</p>\n<p>Main things:<br>\nStoryline: [Discussing];<br>\nScript: [Writing] (1 chapter);<br>\nCode Script: [Writing] (3 code chapters);<br>\nGrids/rooms: [Making] (10 grids);<br>\nArt/images [Making] (1 image);<br>\nDialogues;<br>\nVoices: [Casting] (4 voice actors);<br>\nCharacters and objects: [Testing];<br>\nSounds;<br>\nMusic: [Composing] (1 tune), [Finished casting] (2 composers);<br>\nConcept Art: [Casting] (2 artists) (8 drawings/sketches);<br>\nCoding.</p>\n<p>Things to make during the above items:<br>\nObjects;<br>\nGame flags (inventory items, quests): [According to events/scripts];<br>\nChapters: [Writing] (1 chapter);<br>\nMagic levels: [Decided] (The same as LBA1);<br>\nLocations: [Discussing] (5 locations);<br>\nHolomap Locations;<br>\nDisappearing Grids;<br>\nDialogues and their indexes;<br>\nCharacter names: [Discussing] (8 names);<br>\nCharacters per location: [Discussing];<br>\nActions each character is going to have during the quests;<br>\nCharacter definitions (life points and other properties, and which dialogues is each character going to use);<br>\nModels: [Making] (4 models);<br>\nAnimations;<br>\nSprites and bricks;<br>\nBrick Layout Libraries: [Making] (1 Brick Layout Library);<br>\nTunes (music) [Composing] (1 tune);<br>\nSamples/sounds.</p>\n<p>This thread will be closed and updated when necessary. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
